strings:
<voice_0x01000FEC><se_low>King Trode: At last! At last we can finish off that
despicable Dhoulmagus!

<voice_0x01000FED><se_low>King Trode: Yes, we've been travelling for a long while now. Looking back on all the hard times,
I feel strangely nostalgic...

<voice_0x01000FEE><se_low>King Trode: But this is no time for reminiscing,
you dawdler! This is our chance!
Apparently Dhoulmagus is a bit under
the weather at the moment.
<voice_0x01000FEF><se_low>King Trode: We must give him a good thrashing and lift this diabolical curse!

<voice_0x01000FF0><se_low>King Trode: We'll be waiting here.
I'm sure you won't have any trouble!
